        <item>
            <title>Apple Lightning 未死   Vision Pro 发现「肥版 Lightning」接头</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2024/02/01/lightning/vr-mr-ar/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=lightning</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2024/02/01/lightning/vr-mr-ar/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Pickle Rick]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Thu, 01 Feb 2024 07:00:46 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[VR 科技]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Apple]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Apple Vision Pro]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1218178</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p style="font-weight: 400;">自苹果头戴式显示器 Vision Pro 发布后，其真身一直引人期待，将于美国时间 2 月 2 日正式发售。有 X 的用户发现，Vision Pro 有可能使用了 Lightning 接头。</p><div class="video-container"><blockquote class="twitter-tweet" data-width="500" data-dnt="true"><p lang="en" dir="ltr">Size comparison between the &quot;fat&quot; Lightning plug for the Apple Vision Pro&#39;s battery pack, compared to reg Lightning plug, and second and third pics are compared to USB-C (width) and then top shot to show thickness <a href="https://t.co/tRhUHYOJjl">https://t.co/tRhUHYOJjl</a><a href="https://t.co/7n6UMWhjnA">pic.twitter.com/7n6UMWhjnA</a></p><p>&mdash; Ray Wong (@raywongy) <a href="https://twitter.com/raywongy/status/1752810208278061096?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">January 31, 2024</a></p></blockquote><p><script async src="https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js" charset="utf-8"></script></div><p style="text-align: center;">▲X 用户 <span class="css-1qaijid r-bcqeeo r-qvutc0 r-poiln3">raywongy </span>利用了 SIM 卡针开启了 Vision Pro 电池组的电线，发现其真身是加阔版本的 Lightning 接头</p><p style="font-weight: 400;">X 用户 <span class="css-1qaijid r-bcqeeo r-qvutc0 r-poiln3">raywongy </span>利用了 SIM 卡针开启了 Vision Pro 电池组的电线，发现其真身是加阔版本的 Lightning 接头。在对比之下，加阔版本的 Lightning 接头比向来苹果使用的 Lightning 接头阔近一倍，可提供更强的电量输出。</p><p style="font-weight: 400;">早前，苹果受欧盟规定，迫使其手机及其他装置要使用 USB-C 接头，但 AR/VR 设备并不包含在其中。因此 Vision Pro 则不受限制，可以使用非 USB-C 的接头。</p><p>资料及图片来源：<a href="https://twitter.com/raywongy/status/1752810208278061096?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw%7Ctwcamp%5Etweetembed%7Ctwterm%5E1752810208278061096%7Ctwgr%5Eb76060fe7ff659348d706ec6af0de2adb2b45680%7Ctwcon%5Es1_&amp;ref_url=https%3A%2F%2Ftechnews.tw%2F2024%2F02%2F01%2Fvision-pro-with-lightning%2F">X 用户 <span class="css-1qaijid r-bcqeeo r-qvutc0 r-poiln3">raywongy</span></a></p><br /><b>相关文章:</b><blockquote><li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/01/31/apple-sold-200000-vision-pro-headsets-in-10-days/vr-mr-ar/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">内部消息人士透露   Apple Vision Pro 预售十日销量已达 20 万部</a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/01/30/meta-optimistic-apple-vision-pro-launch/vr-mr-ar/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">对 Apple Vision Pro 感到乐观   Meta 期望借此活化头戴装置市场</a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/01/27/netflix-ceo-explained-no-apple-vision-pro-app/vr-mr-ar/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">程式缺席 Apple Vision Pro   Netflix CEO 解释背后原因</a></li>&nbsp;</blockquote><br /><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/02/01/lightning/vr-mr-ar/">Apple Lightning 未死   Vision Pro 发现「肥版 Lightning」接头</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
]]>
            </description>
